Actually it is display.m in @ThermoPhase that is missing. (The one in 
@Solution was intentionally removed.)
The problem can be fixed by putting the following two-lines file in 
Cantera/matlab/cantera/@ThermoPhase/display.m

-----------cut here-----------------
function display(self)
phase_get(thermo_hndl(self), 15, 1);
-----------cut here------------------



